ğŸŒ Accessing the Applications

Get the Minikube IP:

minikube ip


Example: 192.168.49.2

Add a host entry in /etc/hosts:

192.168.49.2  myapp.local


Access the apps in your browser or curl:

http://myapp.local/frontend
http://myapp.local/backend


If the Ingress doesnâ€™t show an IP, run:

minikube tunnel

